Asking for prayers for my honeyyy💛 it’s been a rough week in and out of the hospital and now he’s back. Long story short, he had what we think is a severe reaction to an antibiotic and has developed thrombocytopenia which causes low blood platelets. Earlier this week they were on the rise and he was sent home but they dropped again, so he is back on steroids and we will see how he responds to those.  Asking for prayers for complete healing, for the right treatment plan from the doctors, for his platelets to not drop more over night, and for the spirit of him and all those who love him to be encouraged and strengthened 💛🙏🏼 #itp #itpawareness
